data.description: Gorgeous 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Home with 2 Car Garage. Granite countertops throughout!! Stainless appliances, Open floor plan. Dual fuel 90% efficient heat pump furnace. Huge Master walk-in closet!! Gas log fireplace with electric start, Raised 10' ceilings completed with crown moldings in living & entryway. Hand textured walls, Double Vanities, jetted master tub, tile shower. Updated with wood look tile flooring in kitchen, living room, dining, and entryway. In Mustang School District!
